Title: Lost in Italy
DateModified: '2019-02-22'
DatePublished: '2019-02-22'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/lost-in-italy
SetInCountry: Italy
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Merry Merry
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: "Hello guys,my name is Merry and I am from Indonesia.I\u2019m gonna share my\
  \ travel story when i was in Italy.my friend and I got reward from Place we work.the\
  \ reward is travelling to Italy for 7 days and we are in group tour.that is the\
  \ first time we go to europe and we feel so excited.there are 2 group tours. On\
  \ the 5th days we got lost at serravalle fashion outlet..the group tours leave us\
  \ because run out of time.the tour leader ask us to use taxi from serravale to milan\
  \ which is quite expensive .the price is around 100 euro and finally we decide to\
  \ ask the staff there is there any bus ,but the bus has leave and the last option\
  \ is use train .we don\u2019t know how to buy the ticket but thanks God there are\
  \ good man helping us to buy ticket,and tell us which train going to Milan.\nWe\
  \ arrived safely at Milan hotel.thanks to the asian man for helping us.\nThats my\
  \ travel story\nThanks for reading"
